api_list.name: Get Company Historical Data
api_list.description:
Provides access to daily historical company pricing data over a given period of months

A sample output for each day:
`{
"changePercent":0
"close":115.1465
"date":"2022-05-27"
"high":115.187
"low":112.628
"open":113.55
"symbol":"AMZN"
"updated":1654726813000
"volume":93660160
}`
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://stoxx1.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/stoxx/company/amzn/history/prices/3"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "stoxx1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
